## Additional Notes

### Storage Architecture Decision

Initially implemented with a separate index (`.opendistro_security_passkey_credentials`), but refactored to use the main security index following the internal users pattern. This:
- Matches established security plugin architecture
- Avoids threading violations (blocking operations on transport threads)
- Simplifies deployment (no additional index to manage)
- Uses proven patterns from `ConfigurationRepository`

